{"tid":1168900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊睇下「東方日報」facebook 讀者嘅高質回應","createTime":"2019-05-24T04:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T05:04:07.000Z","uid":7971,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a83e612a20eef205060b27f98646cbd0f6f1a1b4","tid":1168900,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156865610942655?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F128807942654%2Fposts%2F10156865610942655%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhL32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=62b2e859\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156865610942655?sfns=mo</a><br />\n是咁的 <br />\n有朋友係FB分享咗東方嘅一篇文<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"> <del>平時睇都唔會睇啦</del></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「愈黎愈覺得喺香港生活，真係狗都不如」</span></span><br />\n其實未睇都估到係啲抒情廢up呃like文(下刪100字)<br />\n<br />\n不過重點唔係篇文 <br />\n而係個班新移民、新來港婦女、00後 同 一大班廢老<br />\n我重點抽幾個大家睇下<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n首先熱門第一個 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有姓ZHAO</span></span><br />\n亂用supply同demand<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRhino Zhao<br />\n有人怨收入低，人工少。唔該諗下點解人工低？可能某人懶，可能某人做學生唔讀書，可能某人得罪人多，可能。。。<br />\n<br />\n有人話以前香港生活好 D，快樂 D。某人住過木屋區未？某人試過冇水沖涼，叫樓下刪水喉未？某人試過自己車內衣褲未？另外，以前冇乜人可以 30 歲前去外國旅行喎。。。<br />\n<br />\n有人話政府唔理香港人，樓價貴。我唔否認樓價貴，不過唔該讀下經濟學啦！最簡單 Supply / Demand 嘅道理都用腦諗下啦。E 家唔係政府唔想增加 Supply呀，係香港人自己唔 Q 俾政府增加 Supply 呀。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁多人唔識自省呢！不過我講咁多都係嘥氣，E 個世界有人高 D 、有人肥 D、有人靚仔 D 、當然有人蠢 D。"},{"pid":"d86c3cff80cb20688c0c1322b26f13735042ebf6","tid":1168900,"uid":7971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"再黎多個有係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嶺南大學進修學院</span></span>同學仔<br />\nYik Shing Tsang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種問題都係人為比政府問題多。。。香港算好啦比你差既人多的是呢～最小香港人成9日去旅行就知比好多地方好"},{"pid":"8c8af28de1ec8fca4c05c7675a7dd0618ba5f7b9","tid":1168900,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784cee0b3e214d9da39729c8f3dfbca00c366c25","tid":1168900,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c8af28de1ec8fca4c05c7675a7dd0618ba5f7b9","tid":1168900,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/163758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/163758</a><br />\n呢條仆街成日搭訕，鬧人哋「低端」、聲稱唔會受腥講赤化影響喎～～～～<br />\n<br />\n最新論戰：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1160483\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1160483</a>"},{"pid":"c980c3a670f3c7e1cf681b86d286e9a7b81b1e9a","tid":1168900,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784cee0b3e214d9da39729c8f3dfbca00c366c25","tid":1168900,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c8af28de1ec8fca4c05c7675a7dd0618ba5f7b9","tid":1168900,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/163758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/163758</a><br />\n呢條仆街成日搭訕，鬧人哋「低端」、聲稱唔會受腥講赤化影響喎～～～～<br />\n<br />\n最新論戰：